communications.subject: Freedom of Information Act Request: I/leads
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

All records regarding Edward Alan Monk, birthdate 03-07-1961, WA Drivers License WDL5P335233B.

Including but not limited to * All records of communication used for incidents * * All resources used in cases and investigations * Copies of arrest warrants *Electronic communications, emails, Pen register, internet, telephone and cell phone surveillance, wire or oral communications; Any communications from a tracking device, all gps tracking (ii) Any communication made through a tone-only paging device; all I/LEADS RMS and WACIC entry logs *all Ecommunications with Inter local agencies. All records of communication used for incidents * Command review forms and supervisor reports * All resources used in cases involving " * Copies of arrest warrants * I/LEADS RMS and WACIC entry logs * Emails and communications with Inter local agencies * Incident reports including attachments and vouchers.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Edward Monk
